---
title: Teriyaki Beef & Noodle Stir-Fry with Sesame Seeds & Coriander
description: A quick family meal is within reach with this combination of a speedy teriyaki sauce, satisfying udon noodles and thinly sliced beef strips. Add colourful veggies for a taste of the rainbow and stir-fry your way to happiness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5beba78b30006c1ccb194473-6274190e.jpg
